<br />"<a href="http://pics.pineight.com/dwi/Gay.s3m.zip" class="postlink">Balloon Fever</a>", a cover of the "Balloon Trip" theme from Balloon Fight in the style of "Maximizer" from DDR Extreme (U), uses triplets in the drum fills with the SD2 and SD4 commands. It looks something like this: 
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">C-5 05 v32 ---<br />C-5 05 v20 SD2<br />C-5 05 v20 SD4<br />--- -- --- ---<br />C-5 05 v32 ---<br />C-5 05 v20 SD2<br />C-5 05 v20 SD4<br />--- -- --- ---<br /></div>

		

